## Slide 9 — Multi-Channel Ingestion

### 25+ channels through DigiMe

DigiMe is an OpenClaw-powered AI agent that lives inside messaging apps — it communicates with the memdog RAG system to answer queries, perform semantic search, and ingest data through natural conversation.

| Channel Type | Channels |
|-------------|----------|
| **Messaging** | WhatsApp, Telegram, Signal, iMessage |
| **Team Chat** | Slack, Discord, Matrix, MS Teams |
| **Email** | Gmail, Outlook, IMAP |
| **Social** | Twitter/X, Facebook, Instagram, Reddit |
| **Dev Tools** | GitHub, GitLab, Jira |
| **Cloud Storage** | Google Drive, Dropbox, OneDrive |
| **Other** | RSS, Calendar, Webhooks, REST API |

### 300+ integration platform

OAuth2 and API-key connections to CRM, dev tools, cloud storage, and more — with Fernet-encrypted credentials at rest and a credential-injecting API proxy.

