## Slide 18 — Summary

### memdog is a complete AI memory platform

- **Ingest** from 25+ channels or direct upload (text, files, camera, voice, video)
- **Enrich** with 40 AI agents, 6-layer classification, 5 model tiers
- **Store** with versioning, 10 memory types, knowledge graph, per-user scoping
- **Query** via RAG chat with citations, entity-aware search, semantic similarity
- **Compress** verbose memories into structured summaries
- **Integrate** with LangChain, CrewAI, OpenAI via drop-in adapters
- **Deploy** anywhere: Docker Compose, GKE, Cloud Run, Mac Mini

> **Your data memory, powered by AI.**
